<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6784129>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Coenosia pudurosa Collin, 1953, ♀. A. Detail of wing, ventral view, showing different kinds of macrotrichia: cs = campaniform sensillum; gs = gustatory sensillum; se = setula; sp = spinule. B. Wing, ventral view showing costal sectors 1‒4: CS = costal sector." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6784129/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6784167>
    dc:description "Fig. 18. ♀♀ of Coenosia Meigen, 1826. A. C. intermedia (Fallén, 1825), wing, ventral view. B. Same, detail of wing showing CS1‒3, ventral view. C. Same, detail of wing showing CS1‒3, dorsal view. D. C. emiliae Lukasheva, 1986, detail of wing showing CS1‒3, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6784167/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

